# Defence-in-depth: a decoded copy of the git-crypt symmetric key must
# never land in a commit. The real key lives in 1Password (base64) and
# is loaded into `.git/git-crypt/keys/default` (untracked) by
# `scripts/setup`.
*.gitcrypt-key
gitcrypt.key
gitcrypt.key.bin
